text.tspan: The people part of YOCO Labs have been structuring the feed, make it available as a continuous stream
facilitating the Third Eye to effectively carry out the task of
Face-Match identified a few different appearances of people, along with the repeat & distinct appearances while
earmarking at least some of the suspects as evidences for submission. This has been done under 3 days of
analytical time of the video of a few months' duration. This has been considered as a commendable
achievement for YOCO's team and the client team, while the same had been attempted manually with
several folds of scan time, with slower outcomes. This is where the YOCO Labs' Third Eye has scored.
